I agree wholeheartedly with the request for an oxygen saturation meter. I have asthma and sleep apnea and I'd love to see this addition to an already great application. That's a hardware limitation though I think and the fact that you can even do this on a cellphone with no external hardware is truly a great sign that developers out there are using these devices to their full potential. Keep up the good work and please, add oxygenation levels if at all possible.
